title.rendered: Recopilamos vídeos-pro de Rock In Rio’15: Faith No More, Slipknot, Mastodon, QOTSA, SOAD y Deftones

content.rendered:
Hemos hecho una recopilación de distintas actuaciones en el último Rock In Rio 2015. Aquí os las dejamos junto a su setlist.

 

Faith No More

01 – “Motherfucker”
02 – “From Out Of Nowhere”
03 – “Caffeine”
04 – “Evidence”
05 – “Epic”
06 – “Black Friday”
07 – “Midlife Crisis”
08 – “The Gentle Art Of Making Enemies”
09 – “Easy” (Commodores Cover)
10 – “Separation Anxiety”
11 – “Ashes To Ashes”
12 – “Superhero”
13 – “I Started A Joke” (Bee Gees Cover)
14 – “We Care A Lot”
15 – “Just A Man”

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B8mQjfMicdI

–

Slipknot

01 – “Sarcastrophe”
02 – “The Heretic Anthem”
03 – “Psychosocial”
04 – “The Devil In I”
05 – “AOV”
06 – “Vermilion”
07 – “Wait And Bleed”
08 – “Killpop”
09 – “Before I Forget”
10 – “Sulfur”
11 – “Duality”
12 – “Disasterpiece”
13 – “Spit It Out”
14 – “Custer”
15 – “(sic)”
16 – “People = Shit”
17 – “Surfacing”

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d1jHExK1TrM

–

Mastodon

01 – “Tread Lightly”
02 – “Once More ‘Round The Sun”
03 – “Blasteroid”
04 – “The Motherload”
05 – “Chimes At Midnight”
06 – “High Road”
07 – “Aqua Dementia”
08 – “Halloween”
09 – “Bladecatcher”
10 – “Black Tongue”
11 – “Ember City”
12 – “Crystal Skull”
13 – “Blood And Thunder”

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e5Tpl3mUA_M

–

Queens of the Stone Age

  1. You Think I Ain’t Worth a Dollar, but I Feel Like a Millionaire
  2. No One Knows
  3. My God Is the Sun
  4. Burn the Witch
  5. Smooth Sailing
  6. In My Head
  7. Regular John
  8. Sick, Sick, Sick
  9. The Vampyre of Time and Memory
  10. If I Had a Tail
  11. Little Sister
  12. Fairweather Friends
  13. Go With the Flow
  14. A Song for the Dead

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bfBiGFUhUgk

–

System of a Down

  1. “I-E-A-I-A-I-O”
  2. “Suite-Pee” / “Attack”
  3. “Prison Song”
  4. “Know”
  5. “Aerials”
  6. “Soldier Side – Intro”
  7. “B.Y.O.B.”
  8. “Soil”
  9. “Darts”
  10. “Radio/Video”
  11. “Hypnotize”
  12. “Temper”
  13. “CUBErt”
  14. “Needles”
  15. “Deer Dance”
  16. “Bounce”
  17. “Suggestions”
  18. “Psycho”
  19. “Chop Suey!”
  20. “Lonely Day”
  21. “Question!”
  22. “Lost in Hollywood”
  23. “Vicinity of Obscenity”
  24. “Forest”
  25. “Cigaro”
  26. “Toxicity” (feat. Chino Moreno)
  27. “Sugar”

–

Deftones

  1. Rocket Skates
  2. Be Quiet and Drive (Far Away)
  3. My Own Summer (Shove It)
  4. Tempest
  5. Swerve City
  6. Diamond Eyes
  7. Rosemary
  8. Bloody Cape
  9. Sextape
  10. Change (In the House of Flies)
  11. Passenger (feat. Tim McIlrath)
  12. Engine No. 9
  13. Headup

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=auef63beyJU
